title: Next man up? House GOP pushes reluctant Ryan to seek Speaker's chair
text: Since House Majority Leader Kevin McCarthy shocked his congressional colleagues early Thursday by withdrawing his name from consideration to replace John Boehner as Speaker of the House, Republicans have launched a relentless press aimed at convincing House Ways and Means Committee chair Paul Ryan to put himself forward for the job. ...
